                        <fn>Thomas</fn>
                        <sf/>
                        <pf/>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>A number of Augusta citizens support Michie for the Court of Appeals
                    position.</summary>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
                <column>2</column>
                <head>Col. J.B. Baldwin</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names>
                    <name>
                        <ln>Baldwin</ln>
                        <fn>J.B.</fn>
                        <sf/>
                        <pf/>
                    </name>
                    <name>
                        <ln>Samuels</ln>
                        <fn>Green B.</fn>
                        <sf/>
                        <pf/>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>A number of citizens of Augusta, Rockbridge, and Augusta counties support
