            </div>
            <div type="a">
                <column>3</column>
                <head>Trot Them Round</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Members of the Metropolitan Concert Company left town without paying their
                    bills. Watch out for them!</summary>
            </div>
            <div type="l">
                <column>3</column>
                <head>Meeting at January Court</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The Democracy of Augusta supports a district convention for the nomination
                    of a Democratic candidate for Congress and hopes to participate fully.</summary>
            </div>
