                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Letter from "Old-Line" ridicules meeting of Know-Nothings for electing as
                    head of the meeting a "fat, chunky, old-fashioned Irishman."</summary>
            </div>
            <div type="l">
                <column>3</column>
                <head>We call attention to the communication of our correspondent "Old Line."</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
